Text Template
This template is used to display text data. It can display highlighted text, paragraph text, or table text.

Note!
See Screen UI example for the available display formats of the Text template.


Template field



Field name
Type
Field description
Required




bgUrl
URLObject
The object containing the URL of the image to display in background
No


highlightText
StringObject or NumberObject
When the object contains text or number to highlight, you may add a digit grouping symbol to the number.
No


imageUrl
URLObject
The object containing the URL of the image
No


linkUrl
URLObject
The object containing the URL which redirects to a web map when a map image is included
No


mainText
StringObject
The object containing the main text
No


paragraphText
StringObject
The object containing the paragraph-type text
No


referenceText
StringObject
The object containing the text information of the source
No


referenceURL
URLObject
