No


sentenceText
StringObject
The object containing the sentence-type text
No


subText
StringObject
The object containing the sub text
No


tablieList[]
object array
The object array containing the table-type text. The table has two columns.
No


tablieList[].item1
StringObject
The object containing the text to be displayed in the first column
No


tablieList[].item2
StringObject
The object containing the text to be displayed in the second column
No


tablieList[].item2Link
